<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 09:14:31 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>意大利支持欧盟对中国电动汽车征收关税——政府消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italy-backed-eu-tariffs-china-evs-government-source-2024-07-15/</link><description>一位政府消息人士周一表示，意大利投票支持欧盟对中国电动汽车征收临时关税的举措。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 09:10:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italy-backed-eu-tariffs-china-evs-government-source-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普 T 恤走红：“擦伤，但不茫然”、“传奇永不消亡”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-t-shirts-go-viral-grazed-not-dazed-legends-never-die-2024-07-15/</link><description>唐纳德·特朗普(Donald Trump)未遂暗杀事件引发了一场网络商品热潮，上面印有这位美国总统候选人被枪杀后的照片，标语包括“防弹”、“传奇不死”、“擦过但不晕眩”、“射击”等。让我变得更坚强。”</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 08:48:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-t-shirts-go-viral-grazed-not-dazed-legends-never-die-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国需求疲软，斯沃琪销售额和利润大幅下滑，股价受到重创</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/swatch-sales-profits-slump-weak-china-demand-hammering-shares-2024-07-15/</link><description>全球最大制表商斯沃琪集团周一公布，由于中国奢侈品需求依然疲弱，上半年销售额和盈利大幅下滑，但预计业务将在 2024 年晚些时候大幅改善。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 08:30:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/swatch-sales-profits-slump-weak-china-demand-hammering-shares-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>奥利重新担任尼泊尔五年内第五任总理，承诺政治稳定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/oli-returns-nepals-fifth-pm-five-years-promising-political-stability-2024-07-15/</link><description>资深共产主义政治家 KP 夏尔马·奥利 (KP Sharma Oli) 周一宣誓就任尼泊尔总理，这是五年来的第五任总理，他希望确保这个贫困的喜马拉雅国家的政治稳定，该国迫切需要吸引投资者和创造就业机会。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 07:45:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/oli-returns-nepals-fifth-pm-five-years-promising-political-stability-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>解说：什么是中国的“三中全会”？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/what-is-chinas-third-plenum-2024-07-15/</link><description>中国执政的共产党周一召开了所谓的三中全会，这是一次大约每五年举行一次的重要会议，旨在制定国家长期社会和经济政策的总体方向。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 04:46:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/what-is-chinas-third-plenum-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：特朗普在国债中射击跳弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-07-15/</link><description>Stella Qiu 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 04:36:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>分析师对中国第二季度GDP增长的看法</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/view-chinas-q2-economy-grows-slower-than-forecast-2024-07-15/</link><description>周一的数据显示，中国经济第二季度放缓，房地产市场持续低迷和就业不稳定打压内需，使人们对北京需要推出更多刺激措施的预期依然不减。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 02:39:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/view-chinas-q2-economy-grows-slower-than-forecast-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>中国二季度GDP同比增长4.7% 低于预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-q2-gdp-grows-47-yy-below-forecast-2024-07-15/</link><description>周一官方数据显示，中国第二季度经济同比增长 4.7%，低于分析师预期，尽管政策制定者在房地产长期低迷的情况下寻求提振内需。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 02:18:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-q2-gdp-grows-47-yy-below-forecast-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>中国新房价格跌幅创9年来最快 需要更多支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-june-new-home-prices-fall-fastest-pace-9-years-2024-07-15/</link><description>中国六月份的新房价格以九年来最快的速度下跌，同时房地产销售和投资大幅下滑，这给政策制定者带来了更大的压力，要求他们采取更多刺激措施来支撑遭受重创的行业，因为该行业正在努力寻找底部。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 01:46:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-june-new-home-prices-fall-fastest-pace-9-years-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行维持中期利率不变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-cenbank-leave-medium-term-rate-unchanged-expected-2024-07-15/</link><description>中国央行周一在到期中期贷款展期时，维持中期利率不变。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 01:34:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-cenbank-leave-medium-term-rate-unchanged-expected-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>随着市场转向支持特朗普获胜，美元随加密货币上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-sees-safe-haven-gains-sliding-yen-stays-intervention-watch-2024-07-15/</link><description>唐纳德·特朗普(Donald Trump)在即将到来的美国大选中获胜的交易在美国前总统遭暗杀未遂后升温，美元周一普遍上涨，加密货币也大幅上涨。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 00:53:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-sees-safe-haven-gains-sliding-yen-stays-intervention-watch-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>AI芯片需求激增，台积电第二季度利润跃升30%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-second-quarter-profit-seen-jumping-30-surging-ai-chip-demand-2024-07-15/</link><description>人工智能应用先进芯片的主要生产商台积电周四预计，由于需求飙升，第二季度利润将增长 30%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 00:52:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-second-quarter-profit-seen-jumping-30-surging-ai-chip-demand-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>中国经济步履蹒跚，加大刺激力度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-economy-seen-slowing-q2-stimulus-calls-grow-2024-07-14/</link><description>中国经济第二季度增长速度远低于预期，房地产市场持续低迷和就业不稳定给脆弱的复苏带来了阻碍，让人们对北京需要推出更多刺激措施的预期依然不减。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 23:12:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-economy-seen-slowing-q2-stimulus-calls-grow-2024-07-14/</guid></item><item><title>由于工厂关闭和廉价的中国进口商品，泰国经济面临剧变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/thai-economy-faces-upheaval-due-factory-closures-cheap-chinese-imports-2024-07-14/</link><description>当中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪本月早些时候在泰国开设第一家东南亚工厂时，这个拥有6600万人口的国家成为众人瞩目的焦点，并因其工业愿景而赢得赞誉。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 23:09:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/thai-economy-faces-upheaval-due-factory-closures-cheap-chinese-imports-2024-07-14/</guid></item><item><title>随着市场权衡特朗普攻击的影响，美国国债下滑，美元稳定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-14/</link><description>美元周一保持稳定，而长期美国债券收益率上涨，因投资者权衡总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普的暗杀企图是否会增加他获胜的机会。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 23:03:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-14/</guid></item></channel></rss>